---
// journey-to-the-stars.astro
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Journey to the Stars | Cosmic Astro">
  <article class="blog-post">
    <h1>Journey to the Stars</h1>
    <p>Stars are the building blocks of the cosmos. From their birth in vast nebulae to their explosive demise as supernovae, the life cycle of a star is a captivating story of creation, evolution, and sometimes, destruction.</p>
    <p>In this post, we explore the fascinating processes behind stellar evolution, the forces that shape their destinies, and what these cosmic events tell us about the universe at large.</p>
    <p>Embark on this journey to the stars and uncover the mysteries hidden in the heart of our galaxy.</p>
  </article>
</Layout>

<style>
  .blog-post {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 2rem auto;
    padding: 2rem;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    border-radius: 8px;
    color: var(--text-color);
  }
  .blog-post h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .blog-post p {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
</style>
